Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就是“晴天下雨”的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:57.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,すぐ止むわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:57.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,很快就會停的
