Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いい加減にして！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你有完沒完啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私達はこっちよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我們在這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.80,Monster JP,,0,0,0,,ザケンナー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.80,Monster CN,,0,0,0,,搞事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,すぐ元にもどっちゃう！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,馬上就又恢復原樣了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どうしよう？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:10.86,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:10.86,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保倫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,力を合わせるポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,將力量結合起來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,漲る勇気
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,昂揚之勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,溢れる希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,滿溢之希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光り輝く絆とともに！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,攜光輝璀璨之羈絆 結合與共！
